<p>Toronto, ON M5C 2W5</p>

<p>In your letter, please describe in as much detail as possible, the ways in which you believe that 20 VIC&#39;s Online Privacy Policy has not been complied with. We will investigate your complaint promptly.</p>

<p><br />
Please note that if you provide this 20 VIC website with inconsistent privacy preferences (for example, by indicating on one occasion that third parties may contact you with marketing offers and indicating on another occasion that they may not), 20 VIC cannot guarantee that your most recent privacy preference will be honored.</p>

<p><br />
Also, please note that 20 VIC is not responsible for the content or privacy practices of non-20 VIC websites to which 20 VIC related third party website may link to.<br />
